
# cholesky.hpp

Taken from http://www.guwi17.de/ublas/examples
License agreement is stated in the file, and reproduced below.

# random.hpp

Modified from BOOST numeric_bindings test program:
https://github.com/uBLAS/numeric_bindings/blob/master/libs/numeric/bindings/blas/test/random.hpp
License agreement is stated in the file, and reproduced below.

# expm.hpp

Taken from https://lists.boost.org/MailArchives/ublas/att-2461/expm.hpp
License agreement is stated in the file, and reproduced below.

# determinant.hpp

License agreement requested by email
https://lists.boost.org/MailArchives/ublas/att-2984/det.cpp

# bindings_utils.hpp

Collection of functions put together by Vincent Acary for Siconos from
a variety of test programs from the numeric_bindings directory.  This
file has the same license agreement as numeric_bindings, reproduced
below.

